text_raw:
2. The 6th day of October 2020 is appointed as the day on which the 
Forestry (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 2020 (No. 15 of 2020) shall come into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

5 October, 2020. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 9th October, 2020.
